# Load Libraries
```{r message=FALSE}
library(glue)
library(here)
library(readr)
```

# Setup
```{r}
data_name <- "income"
```

# Read Data
```{r}
clean_data <- read_rds(here(glue("data/clean/{data_name}.rds")))
```

# Wrangle Data
```{r}
wrangle_data <- clean_data
```

# Write Data
```{r}
write_rds(wrangle_data, here(glue("data/wrangle/{data_name}.rds")))
```
